  [LOW] F-DX-02: No pre-commit hooks.
    See F-DEP-04. Formatting errors are caught at lint time (CI) but not
    at commit time. Minor friction for solo developer; important to add
    if the project becomes collaborative.

  [LOW] F-DX-03: portfolio.code-workspace exists but was not audited.
    VSCode workspace settings could include recommended extensions
    (ESLint, Prettier, Tailwind IntelliSense). Verify the file includes
    these to improve onboarding DX.

  [LOW] F-DX-04: No CONTRIBUTING.md or development guide.
    New contributors have no documented steps for running the dev server,
    running lint, or submitting changes. The README covers structure but
    not the development workflow.

